                    <img src="~/images/FourSquare.jpg" alt="Image" class="img-fluid" />
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-6" style="padding-left:180px;">

                    <div class="heading mb-2" style="padding-top:20px; padding-bottom: 40px;">
                        Tips for Four Square:
                    </div>

                    <p>Number of participants:  4 </p>
                    <p>
                        Intensiveness: Moderate
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Suggested Location: Backyard, Parks and Large Public Spaces
                    </p>
                    @*<p>
                            Star Count:
                            <span class="fa fa-star checked"></span>
                            <span class="fa fa-star-half-full"></span>
                        </p>*@


                    <p>
                        Equipment Needed:  1 rubber bounce ball
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Calories Burned: 170 Cal for 30 mins
                    </p>
                    <div class="media-entry h-25">
                        <a href="https://intermountainhealthcare.org/blogs/topics/heart/2015/06/6-kids-games-that-burn-more-calories-than-you-think/#:~:text=Playground%20Games%20%2D%20170%20calories%20(hopscotch,t%2Dball%2C%20etc.)&text=So%20the%20next%20time%20your,So%20get%20out%20and%20play " class="more d-flex align-items-center float-end">
